-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
torch ver 1.8.1 설치 (https://pytorch.org/get-started/previous-versions/)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1) conda install pytorch==1.8.1 torchvision==0.9.1 torchaudio==0.8.1 -f https://download.pytorch.org/whl/torch_stable.html
    
pytorch geometric 맞는 버전 설치. torch1.7, cuda 11.0, --trusted-host=pytorch
    1) pip install torch-scatter -f https://pytorch-geometric.com/whl/torch-1.8.1+cu111.html --trusted-host=pytorch-geometric.com
    2) pip install torch-sparse -f https://pytorch-geometric.com/whl/torch-1.8.1+cu111.html --trusted-host=pytorch-geometric.com
    3) pip install torch-cluster -f https://pytorch-geometric.com/whl/torch-1.8.1+cu111.html --trusted-host=pytorch-geometric.com
    4) pip install torch-spline-conv -f https://pytorch-geometric.com/whl/torch-1.8.1+cu111.html --trusted-host=pytorch-geometric.com
    5) pip install torch-geometric
 
